# GymAI Project Rules

## Always Include in Context

When working on this project, ALWAYS reference and keep in context these documentation files:

1. `documentation/FUNCTIONALITIES.md` - Contains all feature requirements, user roles, MVP phases, and functional specifications
2. `documentation/TECHNICAL.md` - Contains technical requirements, framework options, architecture decisions, and deployment strategies

These files provide the complete context for:
- Understanding feature requirements
- Making technical decisions
- Planning implementation
- Selecting appropriate technologies
- Understanding deployment strategies

## Project Context

This is a cross-platform mobile application (GymAI) for gym and workout management with AI-powered features. Always refer to the documentation files for:
- Feature specifications and requirements
- Technical stack recommendations
- Architecture decisions
- Implementation guidelines

